{"tid":1539640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會動議徹回條例，是否可以被否決？","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:52:18.000Z","uid":166405,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f88edbb2d663cf265ded84a8f6673b8f5d6d784b","tid":1539640,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"剛剛林奠只係話立法會復會後由李家超<span style=\"color: red;\">動議</span>撤回條例<br />\n呢個動議是否可以否決？<br />\n估計林鄭是想分化社會反對聲音，然後大規模政治搜捕與檢控<br />\n壓力一消減既時間再重推送中條例"},{"pid":"565b45cc391cc8cec8fe3756302aadd2afa5f891","tid":1539640,"uid":166405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:13:26.000Z","msg":"推到法律撚修黎！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"afb5d5b50d43619409ee758fb6f2e70c6cc870c0","tid":1539640,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:13:44.000Z","msg":"推到法律撚入黎！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"bea41008a070b2f40aadc01d7f60b5e16328985b","tid":1539640,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:14:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bb29c35f921acbc66740de33c05f24ae33dab3","tid":1539640,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86f559dd77e13617919e083580c803836805cfd","tid":1539640,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:14:23.000Z","msg":"【831 太子站目擊者立法會見記者】<br />\n-有一個人失蹤<br />\n-有機會有一個人死左 比警察打左半個鐘 嘔白泡 差佬見佢冇反應 之後冇打 二三十分鐘後由消防員 非救護人員 送走 完全冇反應<br />\n-差佬同佢地講強姦佢地係正常<br />\n-有被捕人士係警署被非禮 (摸胸)<br />\n-係警署去廁所時不能關門 而當時有其他性別既警員在埋<br />\n-有日本人被捕 警方拒絕比佢聯繫大使館<br />\n-目擊者話傷者係送去瑪嘉烈唔係廣華<br />\n-速龍落電梯 踩住市民背部甚至頭部落"},{"pid":"01a461904480911fe6ba39e8dfff233227655b6b","tid":1539640,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c919d648aacfc28c847b9df0331e31574b076e","tid":1539640,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:14:35.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n林奠唔撚識字，我地教907 908再教佢！"},{"pid":"b0c4cee490bef65e44018d565e2ab5ee766bebe5","tid":1539640,"uid":166405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:14:46.000Z","msg":"法律撚入"},{"pid":"37110fb35058baa4b6b33461afbad6d5563819f2","tid":1539640,"uid":39547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"仆街，只係動議撒回"},{"pid":"5f9827854f8726e8a4a2b86029e5666d2f1ac8c6","tid":1539640,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:15:29.000Z","msg":"根本想拖過人權法 之後否決動議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9683f36d699a99559fc82a9d49fccbec2f50860","tid":1539640,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"64. 法案的撤回或押後處理 <br />\n<br />\n(1) 負責某法案的議員或官員，可在立法會開始就該法案進行二讀或三讀的程序時，宣布撤回或押後處理該法案。 <br />\n(2005年第74號法律公告) <br />\n<br />\n(2) 負責某法案的議員或官員可在符合以下條件的情況下，在立法會開始就該法案進行恢復二讀辯論的程序時，宣布撤回該法案 - <br />\n<br />\n(a) 恢復二讀辯論的目的是為了作出該項宣布；及 <br />\n<br />\n(b) 該目的已在根據本議事規則第54(5)條(二讀)作出恢復二讀辯論的預告中述明。<br />\n(2005年第74號法律公告) <br />\n<br />\n(3) 負責某法案的議員或官員在根據第(2)款宣布撤回該法案時，可就與撤回該法案有關的事宜向立法會發言，但該等發言不容辯論。 (2005年第74號法律公告) <br />\n<br />\n議事規則係寫宣布撤回"},{"pid":"8460dc55be1949f84cbaf316470dba4639b826ed","tid":1539640,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:16:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭宣布撤回送中條例的六大陰謀</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539227</a><br />\n快啲同我入黎睇曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f55b8cd8fed41bf0d765d489eb3e48189cfa41","tid":1539640,"uid":258210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:17:23.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\nbin個袋住先我就同bin個割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb85b059ea6cef447eb7962b2e6557d5bca8de06","tid":1539640,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9683f36d699a99559fc82a9d49fccbec2f50860","tid":1539640,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"64. 法案的撤回或押後處理 <br />\n<br />\n(1) 負責某法案的議員或官員，可在立法會開始就該法案進行二讀或三讀的程序時，宣布撤回或押後處理該法案。 <br />\n(2005年第74號法律公告) <br />\n<br />\n(2) 負責某法案的議員或官員可在符合以下條件的情況下，在立法會開始就該法案進行恢復二讀辯論的程序時，宣布撤回該法案 - <br />\n<br />\n(a) 恢復二讀辯論的目的是為了作出該項宣布；及 <br />\n<br />\n(b) 該目的已在根據本議事規則第54(5)條(二讀)作出恢復二讀辯論的預告中述明。<br />\n(2005年第74號法律公告) <br />\n<br />\n(3) 負責某法案的議員或官員在根據第(2)款宣布撤回該法案時，可就與撤回該法案有關的事宜向立法會發言，但該等發言不容辯論。 (2005年第74號法律公告) <br />\n<br />\n議事規則係寫宣布撤回"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"姐係又玩語言藝術？"},{"pid":"a5cba0a2e6313d7ba9e6074a25c85fe47b3a5ec4","tid":1539640,"uid":23407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:17:46.000Z","msg":"佢頭先話按議事規則動議撤回修例草案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnwC2zr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnwC2zr.png&h=8467c342&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n咁係咪可以有人反對撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f660e15c0a29ea13e4e7c758f07946093f53bca6","tid":1539640,"uid":57532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9683f36d699a99559fc82a9d49fccbec2f50860","tid":1539640,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"64. 法案的撤回或押後處理 <br />\n<br />\n(1) 負責某法案的議員或官員，可在立法會開始就該法案進行二讀或三讀的程序時，宣布撤回或押後處理該法案。 <br />\n(2005年第74號法律公告) <br />\n<br />\n(2) 負責某法案的議員或官員可在符合以下條件的情況下，在立法會開始就該法案進行恢復二讀辯論的程序時，宣布撤回該法案 - <br />\n<br />\n(a) 恢復二讀辯論的目的是為了作出該項宣布；及 <br />\n<br />\n(b) 該目的已在根據本議事規則第54(5)條(二讀)作出恢復二讀辯論的預告中述明。<br />\n(2005年第74號法律公告) <br />\n<br />\n(3) 負責某法案的議員或官員在根據第(2)款宣布撤回該法案時，可就與撤回該法案有關的事宜向立法會發言，但該等發言不容辯論。 (2005年第74號法律公告) <br />\n<br />\n議事規則係寫宣布撤回"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:17:46.000Z","msg":"即係又玩文字遊戲啦。動議=/=宣布<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求．缺一不可<br />\n光復香港．時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"a0e8ba41704a7a284b431bb8b9ea9b18039a5c11","tid":1539640,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r